description: A local teen uncovers her family's secret past and navigates the complicated world of a South African high school.

title: Biohackers
description: A fast-paced thriller following medical student Mia Akerlund who discovers the use of highly advanced biohacking technology in her university town.

title: Dilwale
description: The siblings of two estranged lovers fall for each other, unaware of the violent past that drove them apart.

title: My Next Guest Needs No Introduction with David Letterman
description: Comedian David Letterman interviews people he finds fascinating.

title: AlRawabi School for Girls
description: The bullied outcasts at prestigious Al Rawabi School for Girls plot a series of risky takedowns to get back at their tormentors.

title: Lovestruck in the City
description: Heart stolen by a free-spirited woman after a beachside romance, a passionate architect sets out to reunite with her on the streets of Seoul.

title: How to Become a Tyrant
description: Ruling with an iron fist requires an aspiring dictator to know the playbook for absolute power, as history's despots prove in this sardonic docuseries.

title: Bulgasal
description: The story of a man-turned-immortal, Bulgasal, who wants revenge from a woman with a mysterious past and present, who he deems responsible for his immortality and miseries from the past 600 years, hoping to free himself from his curse.

title: Dragon's Lair: The Movie
description: Dirk the Daring, a knight who sets out to rescue Princess Daphne from the evil dragon Singe and a wizard named Mordroc.

title: Tramps
description: A young man and woman find love in an unlikely place while carrying out a shady deal.

title: I Lost My Body
description: A story of Naoufel, a young man who is in love with Gabrielle. In another part of town, a severed hand escapes from a dissection lab, determined to find its body again.
